rocess requirement in behavior text. Agentic/Workflow are disqualified: no AI model decisions.","test_description":"Instantiate the real persistent queue against test-local storage, configure small capacity, enqueue up to limit, then enqueue one more. Assert overflow enqueue is rejected and persisted size never exceeds configured capacity.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.08,"Integration":0.73,"System":0.17,"Agentic":0.01,"Workflow":0.01}}]}
